title: Meme warfare: Cowboys win this one over Eli Manning and hated NY Giants
text:
By SportsDayDFW.com Contact SportsDayDFW.com on Twitter: @SportsDayDFW 
Though the Cowboys won the NFC East in 2016, the New York Giants were responsible for two of the losses on Dallas' 13-3 ledger. 
So we think a little payback is in order, in the form of meme warfare. Here are some memes from the last several seasons to make you feel better about Cowboys vs. Giants (as if five Super Bowls wasn't enough). 
Enjoy. And don't worry, on-the-field payback is not that far away. This Topic is Missing Your Voice. View Comments
